  "instructions": [
    "cook the quinoa noodles according to package instructions.",
    "in a large skillet, heat the peanut oil over medium-high heat.",
    "add the chicken breast and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "add the diced red onion and cook until translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "add the achiote paste, chili flakes, and cumin. stir to combine.",
    "add the cooked quinoa noodles and stir to combine.",
    "season with salt to taste.",
    "in a small saucepan, melt the dark chocolate chips over low heat.",
    "add the honey and stir to combine.",
    "add the crushed pecans and stir to combine.",
    "pour the chocolate sauce over the noodle mixture and toss to combine.",
    "top with chopped cilantro, if desired.",
    "Ensure poultry is cooked to an internal temperature of 74°C / 165°F (juices run clear, no pink remaining) before serving."
